						<div class="postbody">One suggestion of thing to add could be the octave mode that <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">&lt;</tt> and <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">&gt;</tt> makes the octave permanent while <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">&#39;</tt> and <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">,</tt> makes the octave temporary (a few MML compilers support this).<br /><br />Also, I do not see any description of the <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">mmloctaves</tt> command in the documentation.</div>

					
