					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p214238">Re: Pently: a flexible, space-efficient NES music player</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=214238#p214238"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sun Feb 25, 2018 12:43 am&nbsp;</div></td>
